{"tid":582653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★學徒疑吸煤氣亡 只給死者$500日薪，稱「呢行多數係咁㗎啦」","createTime":"2018-03-06T11:01:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T08:38:51.000Z","uid":19454,"like":31,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"514dfe60af4f4278e97c1c8ce05b67d95049a359","tid":582653,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T11:01:52.000Z","msg":"20歲煤氣技工學徒黃漢民於2015年12月20日，被發現倒斃於東涌一個屋苑地盤的單位內，他疑因吸入煤氣，一氧化碳中毒當場死亡，死因庭今日(6日)續研訊。<br />\n<br />\n死者黃漢民的師傅歐偉光供稱，他於2015年聘用死者為學徒，在涉案地盤工作期間，歐與死者各獲涉案地盤外判商、<span style=\"color: red;\">利安煤氣工程有限公司給予700港元日薪</span>，但歐因死者只是學徒，<span style=\"color: red;\">只給死者500港元日薪，並聲稱「呢行多數係咁㗎啦」</span>，聲稱從未拖糧，每次做完工程後收到工資，就會立刻分發予死者。歐又指帶着死者進入涉事地盤工作約10天後，自己有其他工作，遂留下死者繼續在該地盤工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180306/bkn-20180306164804602-0306_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180306%2Fbkn-20180306164804602-0306_00822_001.html&d=gJNUPDTSKQV1d5aa5ltafiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=f12847ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180306/bkn-20180306164804602-0306_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"62275cf4689faa01195c85b5c8dd1e43e9a8ff00","tid":582653,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T11:03:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2103f8cc70a7df1acde1bf77185b3961dc4210f9","tid":582653,"uid":17606,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T11:04:42.000Z","msg":"係人都知上面大既一定有食水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daabfc29125fd91f2b8969a2310f54db819c7444","tid":582653,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T11:05:05.000Z","msg":"Me too"},{"pid":"56d924618d2254402b07cdb26e606b507bfb92cb","tid":582653,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"daabfc29125fd91f2b8969a2310f54db819c7444","tid":582653,"uid":19552,"